data.description: Discover your dream home! This immaculate 4-bed, 2.5-bath gem, lovingly cared for by a single owner, awaits you. Nestled on a spacious private lot, it boasts a bonus office downstairs and a backyard oasis with a sprawling poured concrete patio, perfect for entertaining. Newer appliances, updated laminate flooring, and recessed lighting. The open concept kitchen flows into the living room. Plus, enjoy the convenience of being mere minutes away from schools, shopping, and major interstates. Don't miss this incredible opportunity!
